{"build_type":"executable","module_name":"worker-parks-across-futex-running-dispatched-member","package_name":"worker-parks-across-futex-running-dispatched-member","description":"A scheduler worker spawned as a thread (entry of a spawn_thread_running_entry). Parks on the futex word at address g_work_futex_addr via FUTEX_WAIT (syscall 202, blocks while the word is 0), then on wake reads the dispatched argument g_work_arg and records it into the shared global g_thread_marker as proof it ran the dispatched work. One-shot for the S1 milestone; the real worker loops. The inline futex is an S1 shortcut; in the full model the futex park is a driver atom.","module_globals":[{"global_name":"g_work_futex_addr","global_type":"i64","global_init":"0"},{"global_name":"g_work_arg","global_type":"i64","global_init":"0"}],"function_definitions":{"worker-parks-across-futex-running-dispatched-member":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"global_read","dest":"futex_addr","name":"g_work_futex_addr"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"suspend-caller-awaiting-doorbell-readiness","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"futex_addr"},{"kind":"var","value":"zero"}],"result_assignment_variable":"r","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"global_read","dest":"arg","name":"g_work_arg"},{"instruction_type":"global_write","name":"g_thread_marker","value":"arg"},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"zero"}}]}}}